# Contents

This repository (knitted HTML linked here: [atmospheric_conductance](https://jadenorli.github.io/eds-230-hw4/code/EDS_230_HW4.html)) implements a simple model of atmospheric conductance and evaluates parameter uncertainity using Sobol sensitivity analysis.
